Package: StudyPrior
Type: Package
Title: Construct Prior Distributions from Historical Information
Version: 0.0.13
Authors@R: c(person("Isaac", "Gravestock", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "isaac.gravestock@uzh.ch",
                      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0283-2065")))
Maintainer: Isaac Gravestock <isaac.gravestock@uzh.ch>
Description: Implements useful prior distributions for incorporating data from previous studies into a new study, such as meta-analytic priors (Schmidli et al.(2014) <doi:10.1111/biom.12242>) and power priors (Gravestock and Held (2018) <arXiv:1708.08239>.
